Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.34,0:00:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(400,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.30,0:00:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Worried that this full tank of energy will lose it's destination
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.57,0:00:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whoever shakes for just a minute their boredom, will explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.71,0:00:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I ride, atop the white line, Oh, Oh, Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.79,0:00:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sit down, in the place you have faith Oh, Oh, Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.80,0:00:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go to the place that tempts you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.19,0:00:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If each person took one thing at a time, freedom and passion in their hand
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.45,0:00:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For the shine to come, continue our journey
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.59,0:00:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unclear everyday trump-card that sustains me, is your soul
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.78,0:01:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The best growth is coming forth, unstoppable wild drive
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.84,0:01:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We are both yet to settle down, striking the door
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.89,0:01:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Damn you Noah... So you've chosen to use cheap methods like kidnapping my brother, Mokuba?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.18,0:01:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I'll get Mokuba back no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.27,0:01:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Daimon, if you insist on getting in my way,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.10,0:01:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll just knock you down\N and continue forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.65,0:01:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if your Deck Master\N is Psycho Shocker,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.19,0:01:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I {\b0}will{\b1} win this Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.90,0:01:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Attack from Space:\N Satellite Cannon"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.12,0:01:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What {\i1}was{\i0} that thing just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.25,0:01:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looked like a rocket or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.55,0:01:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That couldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.88,0:02:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How the heck do I go about telling them that I'm Honda?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.68,0:02:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother, let's continue on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.72,0:02:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to hurry up\N and look for Honda-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.77,0:02:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shizuka-{\i0}chan{\i1}~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.56,0:02:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.02,0:02:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If things go on like this, I'll get to ride in Shizuka-{\i0}chan{\i1}'s arms all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.19,0:02:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shizuka-{\i0}chan{\i1}'s boobs are as soft as candy floss~!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.11,0:02:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're {\i1}so{\i0} soft~!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.41,0:02:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I heard\N Honda-{\i1}kun{\i0}'s voice just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.29,0:02:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.91,0:02:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did we imagine it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.66,0:02:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this happiness can go on,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.71,0:02:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this man, Hiroto Honda, doesn't mind living the rest of his life as a monkey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.09,0:02:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It {\i1}can't{\i0} be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.17,0:02:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This robot...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.38,0:02:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What'dya want?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.34,0:02:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You jerk!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.26,0:02:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're Honda inside this monkey?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.47,0:02:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you disguise\N yourself as a monkey!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.60,0:02:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi, what the hell's this about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.61,0:02:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We still don't know if you're the real Honda-{\i1}kun{\i0}. We can't trust you yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.36,0:02:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.78,0:03:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How else can I prove it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.66,0:03:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I feel kind of sorry for it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.16,0:03:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuka-chan~!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.99,0:03:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knock it {\i1}off{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.54,0:03:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With 3600 points, I'm practically untouchable now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.76,0:03:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lay off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.42,0:03:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.63,0:03:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate\N Injection Angel Lilly's Special Effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.47,0:03:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I give up 1000 Life Points to increase Lilly's Attack Power by 3000 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.94,0:03:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Injection Angel Lilly!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.11,0:03:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for your diagnosis!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.65,0:03:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your injection!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.86,0:03:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll activate\N Dol Dora's Special Effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.29,0:03:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Regeneration Ability, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.79,0:03:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How persistent.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.79,0:03:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set one card on my field.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.30,0:04:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll then activate the Instant Quick-Play Magic, Emergency Rations, from my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.89,0:04:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Emergency Rations allows me to sacrifice my other set cards in exchange for 1000 Life Points per card.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.98,0:04:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.14,0:04:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His Life just increased again...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.77,0:04:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I don't stop his Life Recovery Combo,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.94,0:04:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've got no hope of winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.90,0:04:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All that aside, that card he played sent a rocket into the sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.12,0:04:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The moment he declared "turn end", the lever on that meter raised.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.12,0:04:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what the heck {\i1}is{\i0} that meter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.00,0:04:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.17,0:04:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.21,0:04:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So his friends finally arrived, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.88,0:04:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto, you've got an audience now to watch your last moments.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.60,0:04:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.39,0:04:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no {\i1}way{\i0}\N my brother's going to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.39,0:04:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll be here to save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.35,0:04:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so convinced\N Seto cares about you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.73,0:05:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but what does {\i1}he{\i0} think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.57,0:05:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, look at the Deck Master Kaiba's fighting against.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.20,0:05:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Psycho Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.70,0:05:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then does that mean...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.66,0:05:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0} can't\N use any of his Trap Cards?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.38,0:05:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.21,0:05:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then fighting him is pointless, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.26,0:05:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's true that this Duel was near impossible from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.22,0:05:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But only I can open the path I want to walk with my own strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.47,0:05:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.23,0:05:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daimon, this card will destroy your Life Recovery Combo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.15,0:05:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Card! Heavy Storm!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.69,0:05:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heavy Storm is a card that destroys all Magic and Trap Cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.20,0:05:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you'll lose every Magic and Trap Card on your field!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.20,0:06:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto Kaiba, I'm about to show you that reality is crueler than you think!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.38,0:06:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Counter Trap, activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.75,0:06:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Imperial Command of the Royal Palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.72,0:06:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.30,0:06:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Imperial Command of the Royal Palace is a card that, by the cost of 700 of my Life Points per turn,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.43,0:06:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,negates the effects of all Magic Cards on the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.77,0:06:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now you can no longer activate Magic {\b0}or{\b1} Trap Cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.28,0:06:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.65,0:06:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This ain't good. He just got in an even worse situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.49,0:06:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.62,0:06:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's Daimon for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.70,0:06:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's completely analyzed\N Seto's Dueling style.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.87,0:06:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.96,0:06:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw card.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Life Recovery Combo, activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.51,0:06:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I then initiate Imperial Command of the Royal Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.88,0:06:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, it's time for me to utilize Gozaburo's ultimate weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.10,0:06:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Behold its terrible destructive strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.39,0:06:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.39,0:07:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satellite Cannon, prepare to fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.24,0:07:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.61,0:07:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did that attack come from...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.40,0:07:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.49,0:07:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's correct. The Satellite Cannon is stationed up in space.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.78,0:07:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the ultimate form of weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.08,0:08:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.41,0:08:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way a Monster could attack all the way from up in space!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.46,0:08:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As for Satellite Cannon's Special Ability...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.09,0:08:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It cannot be destroyed by a Level 7 or lower Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.26,0:08:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.01,0:08:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the weakling of a Monster you had on the field wouldn't have had enough Attack Power to stop it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.85,0:08:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when my turn comes to an end,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.78,0:08:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satellite Cannon charges its Attack Energy by 1000 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.15,0:08:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well? How's it feel to be tortured by the great weapon Gozaburo invented!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.83,0:08:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I bore witness on the day you drove Gozaburo to his death!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.29,0:08:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And you will now\N be punished for your crime!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.17,0:08:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For that purpose, you used your innocent little brother Mokuba as if he were a tool!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.17,0:08:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0} did what...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.92,0:08:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! My brother {\i1}used{\i0} me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.30,0:08:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't aware?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.93,0:09:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you'd better keep an open heart as you listen to what he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.93,0:09:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto's {\i1}true form{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.56,0:09:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.23,0:09:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To the day Gozaburo Kaiba set that test up for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.49,0:09:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On that day, you proved you had what it took to be a ruthless business dominator.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.83,0:09:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But your ability to earn such a large sum of money in a small period of time surpassed even Gozaburo's expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.17,0:09:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it more than anything, that day set you off on a path of cruelty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.76,0:09:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Seto-{\i0}sama{\i1}, why did you call the five of us to such a secretive meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.26,0:09:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If the five of you\N work together with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.69,0:09:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}we will be able to steal President Gozaburo's wealth from right under his nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.77,0:09:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How would you like to work with me and take over Kaiba Corporation?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.78,0:10:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We all worked together and began slowly buying Kaiba Corporation stocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.83,0:10:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, we soon ran into trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.33,0:10:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because someone began leaking information of our plan to Gozaburo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.30,0:10:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you put the blame on {\i1}Mokuba{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.76,0:10:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right... That day...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.07,0:10:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Big brother...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.24,0:10:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just how far\N do you think I'll tolerate this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.24,0:10:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Big brother, please believe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.41,0:10:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It wasn't me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.08,0:10:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.25,0:10:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Throw him out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.29,0:10:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the worst day of my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.88,0:11:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feeling hurt and betrayed, the saddened Mokuba went to Gozaburo for comfort.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.93,0:11:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But of course, Gozaburo was only after the two "cards" Mokuba held.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.65,0:11:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With Mokuba's share, Gozaburo held 51 "cards" in his hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.52,0:11:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believing he had won, he stopped buying stocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.99,0:11:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As agreed, it has been one year since our last meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.04,0:11:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As such, I called you hear to discuss something very important.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.46,0:11:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's useless, Seto!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.46,0:11:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know you intend to buy me out,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.71,0:11:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but you only hold 49%.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.84,0:11:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I hold 51% on my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.84,0:11:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As such, I have no intentions of handing over my position as president.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.01,0:11:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Starting right now, Kaiba Corporation declares bankruptcy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.35,0:11:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All our assets will be transferred to a subsidiary!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.23,0:11:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So that makes your stocks worth garbage!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.73,0:11:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You will mortgage your life to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.49,0:12:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and I will continue to hold the title you worked so hard to obtain!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.41,0:12:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.62,0:12:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mokuba...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.53,0:12:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I... I give my two cards to my big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.04,0:12:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.62,0:12:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He disowned you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.58,0:12:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My brother was\N just a bit angry then!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.30,0:12:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mokuba!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.55,0:12:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I won't betray my big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.55,0:12:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In these events, it looks like {\b0}you{\b1} were the one to lose everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.10,0:12:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the very same day, having lost everything he worked so hard for, Gozaburo committed suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.11,0:12:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what are you implying?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.27,0:12:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't {\i1}you{\i0} the one who caused it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.07,0:12:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who leaked\N the plan to Gozaburo...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.11,0:12:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Seto Kaiba! It was {\b0}you{\b1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.12,0:12:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.42,0:12:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You tricked Gozaburo into thinking it was another responsible for leaking the information.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.13,0:13:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You set it up so he had no chance of winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.92,0:13:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you used both Gozaburo and Mokuba to achieve your desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.22,0:13:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You betrayed Mokuba and had him go to Gozaburo for comfort.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.10,0:13:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That was your plan from the start!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.23,0:13:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did all that, knowing Mokuba would return to your side!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.82,0:13:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I just believed in Mokuba.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.03,0:13:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That our bond would {\i1}beat{\i0} Gozaburo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.33,0:13:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Enough excuses, Seto!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.79,0:13:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you imagine how Mokuba felt when you took advantage of his trust and used him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.46,0:13:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you pushed Gozaburo to his death in the same manner!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.55,0:13:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta be kidding...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.59,0:13:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My brother used me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.55,0:13:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you used us, the Big Five, in the same exact way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.56,0:13:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We thought we\N were in on it together at first,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.81,0:14:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but in the end we realized we were just being used by you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.15,0:14:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll pay back that anger in ten-fold!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.24,0:14:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Life is a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.78,0:14:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you crush my dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.20,0:14:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.91,0:14:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Spirit Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.17,0:14:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I switch Dol Doral into Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.96,0:14:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spirit Dragon, attack Lilly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.84,0:14:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spirit Sonic!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.18,0:14:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you gone mad, Seto?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.27,0:14:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate Lilly's Special Ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.11,0:14:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.15,0:14:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not good! If this attack fails, Kaiba's Life Points will hit zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.65,0:14:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm the winner!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.41,0:14:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's not rush here. I activate Spirit Dragon's Special Ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.08,0:14:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For every Dragon-Type Monster I discard from my hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.71,0:15:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spirit Dragon's Attack Power goes up 1000 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.44,0:15:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unreal! You raised your Monster's Attack Power just to spare a few Life Points?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.53,0:15:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0}'s fighting style\N is way too risky!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.24,0:15:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he on a suicide mission?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.03,0:15:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.58,0:15:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's part of Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0}'s plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.66,0:15:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba's plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.21,0:15:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dol Dora, attack Lilly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.80,0:15:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.59,0:15:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have enough Life to activate Lilly's Special Ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.06,0:16:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No~!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.40,0:16:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He runs a deck using a Life Recovery Combo along with his Monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.86,0:16:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if that cycle is disturbed...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.32,0:16:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.87,0:16:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daimon, don't forget to pay 700 Life Points in order to keep Imperial Command of the Royal Palace in effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.63,0:16:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On this turn, I will destroy Imperial Command of the Royal Palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.63,0:16:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now he can use Magic Cards again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.51,0:16:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it! If his cycle is broken when he can't pay Life Points anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.47,0:16:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that begins the self-destruction of his own combo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.14,0:16:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0} has a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.69,0:16:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daimon, if this is the level of your strategical ability, you wouldn't stand a chance running my company.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.36,0:16:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.57,0:16:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn isn't over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.95,0:16:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Monster in Defense Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.74,0:16:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, I fire the Satellite Cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.42,0:17:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.26,0:17:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate Pot of Greed from my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.55,0:17:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using its effect, I draw two cards from my deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.06,0:17:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In addition, I Summon Possessing Blood Soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.32,0:17:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blood Soul, attack his Defense Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.57,0:17:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soul Burning!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.99,0:17:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use! Dream Sprite!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.49,0:17:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dream Sprite's Effect lets me redirect your attack to any other Monster I have on the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.08,0:17:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As such, I switch Blood Soul's attack to target Satellite Cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.55,0:18:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No good! Kaiba's Monster can't reach all the way up into space!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.56,0:18:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.06,0:18:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just one turn and my Satellite Cannon will be charged enough to attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.98,0:18:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And then Seto's Life will hit zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.32,0:18:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.70,0:18:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard! He didn't even attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.49,0:18:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's probably trying to gather its energy to finish the match.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.58,0:18:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satellite can only be attacked by a Monster with over Level 7!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.59,0:18:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Seto, your life ends in just one turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.09,0:18:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible... Getting a Monster higher than Level 7...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.80,0:18:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0} has {\i1}that{\i0} Monster in his deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.47,0:18:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everything is riding on this draw...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.52,0:18:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.98,0:18:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awaken, the blue flame burning within my deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.91,0:19:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You couldn't have...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.28,0:19:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.70,0:19:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon a Monster in Defense Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.33,0:19:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll then activate my Deck Master Ability right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.83,0:19:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord of Dragon's Deck Master Ability allows me to Summon a Dragon Monster from my hand for the cost of 500 Life Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.34,0:19:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll then sacrifice both these Monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.47,0:19:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Two{\i0} sacrifices?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.56,0:19:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to show yourself before us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.19,0:19:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue-Eyes White Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.74,0:19:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aim for space!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.32,0:19:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue-Eyes!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.45,0:19:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue-Eyes is a Level 8 Monster...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.75,0:19:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you {\i1}actually drew{\i0} that Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.21,0:19:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue-Eyes, soar straight through the clouds!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.63,0:20:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the moment you attack Satellite Cannon,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.26,0:20:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this Monster loses its attack strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.01,0:20:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that makes its {\i1}true{\i0} Attack Power...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.68,0:20:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.02,0:20:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.85,0:20:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dreams of creating games won't lose to some weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.32,0:20:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Disappear, ghost of Gozaburo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.61,0:20:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Burst Stream of Destruction!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.72,0:20:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.64,0:20:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba completely turned this around!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.36,0:20:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Mokuba?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.57,0:20:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.69,0:21:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Seto, don't think this is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.62,0:21:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.66,0:21:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My big brother won!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.08,0:21:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba, you don't hate Seto...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.79,0:21:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though he betrayed you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.58,0:21:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I trust in my big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.50,0:21:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how I might feel at the time, it still doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.09,0:21:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.81,0:21:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,MOKUBA!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.65,0:21:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that Kaiba-kun won, that means all five of the Big Five have been defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.19,0:21:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Mokuba-{\i1}kun{\i0} hasn't come back,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.11,0:21:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and Honda's still a monkey.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.53,0:21:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this different from what they promised us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.62,0:21:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0} goes on\N alone to save Mokuba-{\i1}kun{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.91,0:21:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and me and Yugi wind up in Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0}'s old mansion while following him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.46,0:22:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what we find there...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.21,0:22:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.75,0:22:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Mystery Deepens: Noah's True Colors"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.05,0:22:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.04,0:22:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unsinkable sun, wherever it rises
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.95,0:22:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A dream is a dream, and it won't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.22,0:22:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The straight rail and the steep route
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.90,0:22:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To go, or not go all of yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.29,0:22:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm getting tired of counting my advances in a cage
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.85,0:22:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Respect! Boys, show me your strength
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.44,0:22:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's awkward, but draw the map
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.21,0:22:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now let's walk forever with our head up high...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.36,0:23:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unsinkable sun, if it starts to get to familiar like you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.17,0:23:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}answer freely to the everyday discomfort
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.95,0:23:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to believe you, because I am losing my way with everything
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.93,0:23:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hiding in my heart... this secret paradise
